TEXT(&beginproblem);
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,6,1);
$funct = "-cos(e^($a * x))";

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Evaluate the indefinite integral.
$BR \[ \int $a e^{$a x} \sin (e^{$a x}) \, dx \]
